dct_description_sm: Relief shown by 5 feet contour interval and spot heights. Map shows provincial, district, planning area, municipal or township, property and cadastral boundaries, mosques, cemeteries. "Cadastral boundaries as shown on this map do not in any way affect the boundaries shown in Registered Titles." Includes index to sheets. "(N. A. 36, V. II. 43⁷)." "Surveyed (May 1961) and drawn (September 1961) by Lands & Surveys Department, Uganda." "Crown copyright reserved." "The representation on this map of a road, track or footpath is no evidence of the existence of a right of way." "200-11-61."
dct_creator_sm: Uganda. Department of Lands and Surveys
